RECOMMENDED VAxAI ENTRY: Training + policy guidance

WHY ADMIN / AI PRESSURE IS HIGH:
Health and wellbeing delivery needs appointment coordination, clinical liaison and case records.

CHARITY / SECTOR AI CONTEXT (use in conversation):
Health charities must balance efficiency with clinical governance. AI training and workflow review around non-clinical admin (scheduling, reporting drafts) is usually the safest entry point.

WHERE VA ALONE IS NOT THE RIGHT LEAD:
Do not propose AI for clinical decisions or patient triage — focus on administrative coordination and governed drafting support.

STRONGEST REASON TO CONTACT:
TAMESIDE SPORTS TRUST shows health & wellbeing delivery with material admin load — Identify admin tasks that can be AI-assisted without clinical risk

